ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectStony Plain Indian Reserve No. 135 (Alberta) ** Reserve Name Change **
PrecisOrder approving the CHANGE OF NAME OF A RESERVE from the Stony Plain Indian Reserve No. 135 to ENOCH CREE NATION No. 135 for the Enoch Cree Nation, in Alberta. The reserve is located in the County of Parkland.
